¬import il from "../../../_shared/variables/imageLinks"


## Download vscode

1. In the browser address bar type *https://code.visualstudio.com/* and presee the **Return** key on the keyboard. *- red circle* 
2. The vscode website is displayed.
3. Click the **Download** button. *- yellow circle* 

{{::il.Firefox_vscode_img}}

4. The download page is displayed and the download starts.
5. When vscode has finished downloading the browser should show notify you like Firefox does in image below. *- red circle* 
6. Click the downloaded file to run the installer. *- yellow circle* 

{{::il.Firefox_vscode_downloaded_img}}

